quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  6,60,"Òun ni Ẹni tó ń kùn yín ní oorun ní alẹ́.<sup>1</sup> Ó sì nímọ̀ nípa ohun tí ẹ ṣe níṣẹ́ ní ọ̀sán. Lẹ́yìn náà, Ó ń gbe yín dìde (fún ìjẹ-ìmu) ní (ọ̀sán) nítorí kí wọ́n lè parí gbèdéke àkókò kan. Lẹ́yìn náà, ọ̀dọ̀ Rẹ̀ ni ibùpadàsí yín. Lẹ́yìn náà, Ó máa fún yín ní ìró ohun tí ẹ̀ ń ṣe níṣẹ́.","[1] Ismul-mọsdar “yatawaffākum” ni “wafāt”. Ní àyè yìí “wafāt” kò sì túmọ̀ sí ikú bí kò ṣe oorun. Bákan náà, “wafāt” ni ismul-mọsdar “tawaffat-hu” nínú āyah 61 níwájú. Òhun sì túmọ̀ sí ikú."
  6,61,"Òun ni Olùborí tó wà lókè àwọn ẹrú Rẹ̀.<sup>1</sup> Ó sì ń rán àwọn ẹ̀ṣọ́ kan (nínú àwọn mọlāikah) si yín títí di ìgbà tí ikú yóò fi dé bá ẹnì kọ̀ọ̀kan yín. Àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ wa yó sì gba ẹ̀mí rẹ̀, wọn kò sì níí jáfira.","[1] Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al-Mujādilah; 58:7."
  6,62,"Lẹ́yìn náà, wọ́n yóò dá wọn padà sí ọ̀dọ̀ Allāhu Olúwa wọn Òdodo. Kíyè sí i, tiRẹ̀ ni ìdájọ́. Ó sì yára jùlọ nínú àwọn olùṣírò.<sup>1</sup>","[1] Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah as-Sọ̄ffāt; 37:125."
  6,63,"Sọ pé: “Ta ni ẹni tó ń gbà yín là nínú òkùnkùn ilẹ̀ àti ibúdò, Ẹni tí ẹ̀ ń pè pẹ̀lú ìrawọ́rasẹ̀ àti ní ìkọ̀kọ̀ pé: “Dájúdájú tí Ó bá gbà wá là nínú èyí, dájúdájú àwa yóò wà nínú àwọn olùdúpẹ́ (fún Un)?”",""
  6,64,"Sọ pé: “Allāhu l’Ó ń gbà yín là nínú rẹ̀ àti nínú gbogbo ìbànújẹ́. Lẹ́yìn náà, ẹ tún ń ṣẹbọ.”",""
  6,65,"Sọ pé: “Ó lágbára láti fi ìyà ránṣẹ́ si yín láti òkè yín tàbí láti ìsàlẹ̀ ẹsẹ̀ yín, tàbí kí Ó dà yín pọ̀ mọ́ onírúurú ìjọ, nítorí kí Ó lè mu apá kan yín fìnira kan apá kan. Wo bí A ṣe ń mú àwọn āyah wá lóníran-ànran ọ̀nà nítorí kí wọ́n lè gbọ́ àgbọ́yé.”",""
  6,66,"Àwọn ènìyàn rẹ pe al-Ƙur’ān nírọ́! (Àmọ́) òdodo ni. Sọ pé: “Èmi kì í ṣe olùṣọ́ lórí yín.”",""
  6,67,"Gbogbo ìró (àsọtẹ́lẹ̀) l’ó máa wá sí ìmúṣẹ. Láìpẹ́ ẹ máa mọ̀.",""
  6,68,"Nígbà tí o bá rí àwọn tó ń sọ ìsọkúsọ nípa àwọn āyah Wa, nígbà náà ṣẹ́rí kúrò ní ọ̀dọ̀ wọn títí wọn yóò fi bọ́ sínú ọ̀rọ̀ mìíràn. Tí aṣ-Ṣaetọ̄n bá ń mú ọ gbàgbé (tẹ́lẹ̀), ní báyìí lẹ́yìn ìrántí má ṣe jókòó ti ìjọ alábòsí.",""
